# Step 1: Dockerfile

## File: `docker/Dockerfile`

```dockerfile id="c7pjlwm"
FROM python:3.11

WORKDIR /app

COPY . .

RUN pip install -r requirements.txt

CMD ["python", "src/api/app.py"]
```

---

# Build Docker Image

```bash id="wjlwmf"
docker build -t high-performance-app .
```

---

# Run Docker Container

```bash id="cqeq4q"
docker run -p 5000:5000 high-performance-app
```

---

# Step 2: Kubernetes Deployment

## File: `kubernetes/deployment.yaml`

```yaml id="7p4nh5"
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment

metadata:
  name: high-performance-app

spec:
  replicas: 2

  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: high-performance-app

  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: high-performance-app

    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: high-performance-app
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5000
```

---

# Deploy to Kubernetes

```bash id="jlwm1n"
kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
```

